import React from 'react'
import {Container, Row, Col, Modal,Form, Button} from 'react-bootstrap';


const RegisterForm = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Form>
    <Form.Group as={Row} className="mb-3" controlId="first_name">
        <Form.Label column sm={3}>
          First Name
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm={9}>
          <Form.Control type="text" name='first_name' placeholder="First Name" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group as={Row} className="mb-3" controlId="email">
        <Form.Label column sm={3}>
          Last Name
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm={9}>
          <Form.Control type="text" name='last_name' placeholder="Last Name" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group as={Row} className="mb-3" controlId="email">
        <Form.Label column sm={3}>
          Email
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm={9}>
          <Form.Control type="email" name='email' placeholder="Email" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group as={Row} className="mb-3" controlId="phone_number">
        <Form.Label column sm={3}>
          Phone Number
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm={9}>
          <Form.Control type="tel" name='phone_number' placeholder="Phone Number" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group as={Row} className="mb-3" controlId="password">
        <Form.Label column sm={3}>
          Password
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm={9}>
          <Form.Control type="password" name='password' placeholder="Password" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
    <fieldset>
        <Form.Group as={Row} className="mb-3">
          <Form.Label as="legend" column sm={3}>
            User Type
          </Form.Label>
          <Col sm={9}>
            <Form.Check
              type="radio"
              value="1"
              label="Buyer"
              name="user_type"
              id="buyer"
            />
            <Form.Check
              type="radio"
              value="2"
              label="Seller"
              name="user_type"
              id="seller"
            />
          </Col>
        </Form.Group>
      </fieldset>
      <Form.Group as={Row} className="mb-3">
        <Col sm={{ span: 10, offset: 2 }}>
          <Button type="submit">Sign in</Button>
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
        </Form>
    </>
  )
}

export default RegisterForm
